item.title: dream helped Batman
item.description: ##08:16 Sunday 02 December 2012 The Joker tossed the head of her husband through the window. She looked in horror as it spoke to her, like, “surprise!!” and I saw attached a canister with poison gas spewing out; she got covered in gas and her head popped off and her face sunk into a spherical glass shell the size of her skull and rolled back toward The Joker; her head had become a bomb for his next target.
